metadata.name: Americana
metadata.description:
From my most distant childhood memory, in the 80's, the americana (high tops) are my first shoes that I loved. Much later when they made their big comeback I switched to bass.
It's this model that I illustrated.  It is only natural that I start with this one to open the new NFT collection… 

-
 Size: 5906*8268 px | 300dpi
